to the police.

28:25.470 --> 28:27.062
No, you'd never make it.

28:27.105 --> 28:28.595
They'll be watching
all the precincts...

28:28.640 --> 28:30.938
probably got some of the boys in blue
on payola too.

28:45.457 --> 28:47.015
I've rounded up 50 guys.

28:47.058 --> 28:48.753
Well, I guess that's just
gonna have to do, huh?

28:57.969 --> 29:00.403
Stop the car. He was here.

29:00.438 --> 29:02.303
Come on, what makes
you think he was here?

29:02.340 --> 29:05.104
Trust me. I know what people do
and I know what people think.

29:05.143 --> 29:08.601
I always have.
Even as a kid, I had this gift.

29:08.646 --> 29:10.910
Yeah, you shoulda seen
the playground hurt I laid down...

29:10.949 --> 29:12.917
playin' rock, paper, scissors, buddy.

29:12.951 --> 29:15.112
Now stop the car.

29:16.221 --> 29:18.416
Who do you think
wants this baby dead?

29:18.456 --> 29:20.754
I've no idea who's tryin' to kill it.

29:20.792 --> 29:22.623
Don't call him an "it."

29:22.660 --> 29:24.321
It's an "it" to me.

29:28.333 --> 29:31.268
Tell me, Smith,
is there anything you like?

29:31.302 --> 29:33.429
Yeah, my privacy.

29:38.176 --> 29:40.838
Tell me something I don't know
<i>per una volta...</i>

29:40.879 --> 29:42.278
<i>brutto figlio di puttana bastardo.</i>

29:42.313 --> 29:44.838
I love it when you talk like that.

29:45.784 --> 29:47.615
Can I offer you anything?

29:49.254 --> 29:50.653
Carrot?

29:52.190 --> 29:54.124
It's good for your eyesight.

29:58.997 --> 30:00.464
Of all the squats in the city...

30:00.498 --> 30:02.432
how does he know
Smith's in this one?

30:02.467 --> 30:04.059
Another lucky guess?

30:04.102 --> 30:05.865
Nah, he doesn't guess.

30:05.904 --> 30:07.838
He sees things we don't.

30:07.872 --> 30:10.864
He was once an FBI profiler.

30:10.909 --> 30:13.776
Forensic behavior consultant.

30:13.812 --> 30:16.781
My god, how many times
do I have to tell you guys?

30:16.815 --> 30:18.282
Details...

30:19.818 --> 30:23.379
...make all the difference
in this business.

30:23.421 --> 30:24.945
Hey, but...

30:25.857 --> 30:27.950
Don't... you think
you should hang back, sir?

30:27.992 --> 30:30.927
The leader who stays in the rear,
takes it in the rear.

30:35.733 --> 30:37.598
Besides...

30:41.973 --> 30:44.703
violence is one of
the most fun things to watch.

30:45.743 --> 30:47.040
No, no, no, baby, no.

30:47.078 --> 30:48.739
We could call him Oliver.

30:48.780 --> 30:51.340
- Oliver?
- Yeah, like Oliver Twist.

30:51.382 --> 30:53.077
Because he's an orphan?

30:53.117 --> 30:54.243
'Cause I like the book.

30:54.285 --> 30:56.378
- You like the book.
- I didn't hate it.

30:56.421 --> 30:58.116
That's a first.

31:03.294 --> 31:05.990
Which birthday card do
you think I should go with here?

31:06.998 --> 31:08.556
Cute and cuddly?

31:09.133 --> 31:12.159
Or the one that says,
"You're becomin' a man now, son"?

31:15.874 --> 31:17.535
So, Mr. Hertz?

31:17.575 --> 31:18.974
How old is your son?

31:19.010 --> 31:20.568
He's 8.

31:20.612 --> 31:23.012
Then it had to be
large and powerful and...

31:23.915 --> 31:25.542
Can you believe it?

31:25.583 --> 31:26.675
There's nothing on the TV...

31:26.718 --> 31:28.379
- about any of this.
...without a trace.

31:32.223 --> 31:33.781
...roadside bomb wounded...

31:33.825 --> 31:35.019
We have it in our...

31:37.862 --> 31:40.126
Hey. Do you notice that?

31:40.164 --> 31:41.597
Notice what?

31:41.633 --> 31:43.396
Look.

31:43.434 --> 31:47.894
Lame-ass politician rants about
gun control, he cries.

31:49.173 --> 31:50.435
- So tonight...
- Switch to this channel...

31:50.475 --> 31:51.635
with this heavy metal music...

31:54.112 --> 31:55.204
...he shuts up.

31:56.414 --> 31:57.847
That's so weird.

32:01.219 --> 32:03.881
He must find it comforting.

32:03.922 --> 32:05.389
- Sir?
- Yeah?

32:05.423 --> 32:09.052
- Men are in place on the roof.
- That's good.

32:09.093 --> 32:12.551
Anybody know what a
Jimmy Cagney love scene is?

32:13.698 --> 32:15.791
It's where Cagney
lets the good guy live.

32:20.004 --> 32:23.735
And if that happens in this show...

32:23.775 --> 32:26.437
I'm gonna do a lot more
than ask for my money back.

32:26.477 --> 32:30.538
All right? Let's kill this mother. go.

32:33.818 --> 32:37.015
It doesn't surprise me that
Oliver's into death metal.

32:37.055 --> 32:38.750
Look at his surrogate parents.

32:38.790 --> 32:41.452
No, I'm telling ya, this means...

32:43.361 --> 32:44.760
go. Back way.

32:55.373 --> 32:56.601
# If you like to gamble #

32:56.641 --> 32:58.336
# I tell you I'm your man #

32:58.376 --> 33:02.142
# You win some, lose some,
it's still the same to me #

33:08.786 --> 33:10.481
# Playing for the high one #

33:10.521 --> 33:11.681
# Dancing with the devil #

33:11.723 --> 33:13.816
# going with the flow #

33:13.858 --> 33:15.792
# It's all a game to me #

33:22.066 --> 33:23.863
# Seven or eleven #

33:23.901 --> 33:25.801
# Snake eyes watching you #

33:29.007 --> 33:30.702
